Class VariableList.ScopeVariableList

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.nsc.de.compiler.interpreter.VariableList

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Enclosing class:
    VariableList

    public static class VariableList.ScopeVariableList
extends VariableList
    This is a VariableList that forces all of its children to use a scope, it is required for the implementation of VariableList.withScope(Scope)
    Author:
    Nicolas Schmidt
